            . I live in <placeName id="t18140914-69-crimeloc381">Gray's-inn-lane, No. 120, in the parish of St. Andrew's, Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18140914-69-crimeloc381" type="placeName" value="Gray's-inn-lane, No. 120, in the parish of St. Andrew's, Holborn"></interp>
