                  Joe 
                  Golding
               <interp inst="t18140914-69-person699" type="surname" value="Golding"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18140914-69-person699" type="given" value="Joe"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18140914-69-person699" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             were talking together. The prisoner said with an oath, it would not do to stand there, the traps were after him, meaning the officers were after him. I asked him what for; the prisoner nudged 
               <persName id="t18140914-69-person700">
                  Joe 
                  Golding
               <interp inst="t18140914-69-person700" type="surname" value="Golding"></interp>
